# InfinityTrain Environment Variables

# For production deployment on Render with Supabase
# Add these in Render Dashboard → Environment Variables

# Supabase Configuration
# Get these from: Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# Note: If these are not set, the app will use SQLite (local file database)
# Perfect for local development!
